<br>
It's certainly not easy, but I wouldn't say you have no time to chat.  During downtime, you put on clarity if your group is caster heavy, or regen if all the group is hurt, and you take a break.  We chat a lot, but we chat in spurts.  During fights, all our attention is on the fight.  Between fights, we heal and crack our group up, and re-think our current song selection..<br>
<br>
