<br>
Bards only have the ability to play one song at a time. But a feature of the songs was that when the bard stops playing a song it lasts for about a few ticks afterwards, while is flashes. So, a bard is able to switch songs quickly in order to get multiple songs flashing at the same time. This means that they could cycle though their songs at such a rate that they could &quot;Twist&quot; two or more songs.  Playing a bard is very hard on your hands. <br>
